cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Conditional Random Fields (CRFs) for this task also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of graph cuts, which is a common optimization technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and computational geometry (cs.CR).
